bien: everything is all right.

11 tant mieux: so much the better.

12 Tuzenbakh: Van recites the last words of the unfortunate Baron in Chekhov’s Three Sisters who does not know what to say but feels urged to say something to Irina before going to fight his fatal duel.

1 kontretan: Russian mispronunciation of contretemps.

2 kameristochka: Russ., young chambermaid.

3 en effet: indeed.

4 petit nègre: little Negro in the flowering field.

5 ce sera etc.: it will be a dinner for four.

6 Wag